data.description: Large rural farmstead offering peace, quiet, and private living down a 3/4 mile drive. Enjoy 91 acres of woods: perfect to hike, camp, fish (pondand stream), hunt (deer, goose, duck, and more). 13 cleared acres: raise sheep, cows, horses, chickens ... or just enjoy the space as you see fit. Then jumpin the saltwater pool! ---- The house is a beautiful custom build. Huge windows with an overlook. 1st floor master with walk-in huge shower, heated floorsand towel rack. Live downstairs but with 2 additional beds on 2nd floor. Enjoy the day on your spacious decking. ---- Extras: whole house generator, heatedmaster bath flooring/towel rack, tile/wood mix, metal roof, water softener. Plenty of outbuildings and shelters. RV parking pad with RV electric hookup. 5water points. 3 electric points. Separate AC'ed office in the tool barn.
